# Components

## Folders
`layout/` · `ui/` · `sections/` · `content/` · `seo/` · `studio/`

Route-private UI: `app/(site)/**/_components/` — never imported elsewhere  
(e.g. `contact/_components/ContactForm.tsx`)

Shared listings: `content/NestedChildListing`  
Portable Text: `content/RichTextBody` (wraps `TW_RICH_TEXT_*` — not raw `PortableText` in pages)  
Client forms: `ui/TurnstileField` · route-private `contact/_components/ContactForm`

## Patterns
- `Header` + lazy `HeaderMobileMenu` (`dynamic`, `ssr: false`)
- Footer: inline SVG in RSC; lucide in client components only
- `role="menuitem"` only inside dropdown `role="menu"`
- LCP exception: hero native `<img fetchPriority="high">`
- Pass Sanity data as props; batch layout reads in rAF

